This is a jolokia demo.
use the next technology: spring, jolokia

If you want to build this project, please follow the next step.
1, checkout out parent and run: 
    git clone git@github.com:bulain/parent.git
    mvn install
2, checkout out jolokia-demo and run: 
    git clone git@github.com:bulain/jolokia-demo.git
    mvn eclipse:eclipse
    mvn jetty:run
    mvn jetty:run -Pit
    mvn package
    mvn verify -Pit
   

Example URL:
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/search/*:*
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/search/java.lang:*
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/search/jolokia:*
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/search/jolokia:name=*
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/list/jolokia/name=JmxBean
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/read/jolokia:name=JmxBean/Times
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/write/jolokia:name=JmxBean/Times/2
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/exec/jolokia:name=JmxBean/resetTimes
http://localhost:8082/jolokia-demo/jolokia/exec/jolokia:name=JmxBean/addTimes/3




